metadata.name: Doggystyle, #1
metadata.description:
This is Bruno from series "Doggystyle", 2021 by Koekkoek

Doggystyle is not only the debut studio album by American rapper Snoop Doggy Dogg. It's also the title of 2022 dog-art collection by Daniel Gebhart de Koekkoek. Featuring dogs with style.

This body of work was also featured on CNN, It's Nice That, Vogue, and Wallpaper.
